content:
Enable Work Summaries

To get started, turn on Work Summaries.

Available in: Lightning Experience, Enterprise and Unlimited Editions with the Einstein for Service add-on

USER PERMISSIONS NEEDED
View Setup and Customize Application to build and manage Einstein Case Classification and Einstein for Service: Work Summaries.
Turn on Einstein Generative AI to use generative AI with Einstein for Service: Work Summaries.

From Setup, enter Work Summaries, select Einstein Work Summaries, and turn it on.
title: Enabling Work Summaries in Service Cloud
